OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F444A1778170273
OL,3,CPastor guilty of 'abortion safe zone'
OL,4,Cprotest
OL,6,FA pastor has been found guilty of
OL,7,Fconducting an illegal abortion protest
OL,8,Finside the limits of a 'safe access
OL,9,Fzone'.
OL,11,FClive Johnston, from the Melmount Road
OL,12,Fin Sion Mills and who is a former
OL,13,FPresident of the Association of
OL,14,FBaptist Churches in Ireland, faced two
OL,15,Fcharges under the Abortion Services
OL,16,F(Safe Access Zones) Act (Northern
OL,17,FIreland) 2023.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/9
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,445,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F444A1778170273
OL,3,CPastor guilty of 'abortion safe zone'
OL,4,Cprotest
OL,6,FThe 77-year-old retired pastor was
OL,7,Faccused of doing an act in a safe
OL,8,Faccess zone at the Causeway Hospital
OL,9,Fin Coleraine, "namely conducted a
OL,10,Fprotest with the intent of, or being
OL,11,Freckless as to whether, it had the
OL,12,Feffect of influencing a protected
OL,13,Fperson whether directly or indirectly,
OL,14,Fin connection with the protected
OL,15,Fperson attending the premises," on 7
OL,16,FJuly 2024.
OL,18,FThe pensioner was further charged that
OL,19,Fon the same date he "failed to comply
OL,20,Fwith a direction...to leave a safe
OL,21,Faccess zone."
OL,26,@qD@OOUwD@_O]{D@UOU}D@MO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/9
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,445,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F444A1778170273
OL,3,CPastor guilty of 'abortion safe zone'
OL,4,Cprotest
OL,6,FIn his defence, Johnston said he was
OL,7,Fnot protesting, but rather, he was was
OL,8,Fgiving a sermon and spreading the
OL,9,FGospel.
OL,11,FRuling today at Coleraine Magistrates'
OL,12,FCourt Judge Peter King found Johnston
OL,13,Fguilty on both counts and fined
OL,14,FJohnston #450.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/9
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
