CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F444A1778170273
OL,3,CPastor guilty of 'abortion safe zone'
OL,4,Cprotest
OL,6,FUnder The Abortion Services (Safe
OL,7,FAccess Zones) Act (Northern Ireland)
OL,8,F2023, which received Royal Assent on 6
OL,9,FFebruary 2023, anti-abortion protests
OL,10,Fand other behaviours are prohibited
OL,11,Fwithin any Safe Access Zone once it
OL,12,Fhas been established, and this may be
OL,13,Fenforced by the PSNI.
OL,15,FIt was the prosecution case that the
OL,16,Fdefendant either intended to
OL,17,Finfluence, or was reckless as to
OL,18,Fwhether any "protected person"
OL,19,Fattending the Causeway Hospital
OL,20,Fabortion services, would be influenced.
OL,26,@zD@MOUzD@^O]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G4/9
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,445,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F444A1778170273
OL,3,CPastor guilty of 'abortion safe zone'
OL,4,Cprotest
OL,6,FThe court heard evidence and watched
OL,7,Ffootage from police body worn cameras,
OL,8,Fthat the retired pastor, standing
OL,9,Fclose to a large crucifix, was using a
OL,10,Fmicrophone as he quoted passages from
OL,11,Fthe Bible.
OL,13,F"We are giving the word of God," Mr
OL,14,FJohnston is heard telling a police
OL,15,Finspector, "I want the government to
OL,16,Fknow that there is a higher law."
OL,26,@uD@AOUuD@`O]wD@LOUxD@aO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G5/9
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,445,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44406
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F444A1778170273
OL,3,CPastor guilty of 'abortion safe zone'
OL,4,Cprotest
OL,6,FGiving evidence on his own behalf, the
OL,7,F77-year-old maintained that although
OL,8,Fhe had objections to the laws which
OL,9,Fextended abortion services to NI, he
OL,10,Fwas not protesting outside the
OL,11,Fhospital on 7 July last year but
OL,12,Frather, he was giving a sermon and
OL,13,Fspreading the Gospel.
OL,15,FHe lamented that if it has come to a
OL,16,Fstage where spreading the "light of
OL,17,FJesus" is not allowed and is now
OL,18,Fillegal, "then in our country we have
OL,19,Fcome to a very sad position."
OL,26,@xD@[OUyD@FO]zD@JOU{D@]O]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G6/9
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,445,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44407
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F444A1778170273
OL,3,CPastor guilty of 'abortion safe zone'
OL,4,Cprotest
OL,6,FHowever, prosecutors argued that the
OL,7,Foffence was made out given the
OL,8,Fcontext, the location, the cross being
OL,9,Fpresent and that the group were
OL,10,Fsinging gospel songs.
OL,12,FThe purpose was not to conduct a
OL,13,Freligious service but rather the
OL,14,Fmessage was a "pro-life, anti abortion
OL,15,Fone," the prosecuting barrister
OL,16,Fcontended.
OL,26,@vD@OOUwD@EO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G7/9
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,445,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44408
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F444A1778170273
OL,3,CPastor guilty of 'abortion safe zone'
OL,4,Cprotest
OL,6,FHe told the court he wanted to make it
OL,7,F"very clear... there is no prohibition
OL,8,Fon holding a religious service, except
OL,9,Fby the legislation in this very
OL,10,Flimited location."
OL,12,FIt was argued Johnston had chosen to
OL,13,Fconduct his service at that particular
OL,14,Fpoint, because the clinic was there
OL,15,Fand that he would not have been there
OL,16,Fif not for the presence of the clinic.
